data.title: Detailed information for TurboTax
data.text:
Company name:

Intuit Canada

Product names:

TurboTax (Windows) Certified for the 2018 to 2023 tax years

TurboTax Free (Windows) Certified for the 2018 to 2022 tax years

Support:

turbotax.ca/support

Available services:

Auto-fill my return – 2018 to 2023 tax years

Express Notice of Assessment – 2018 to 2023 tax years

ReFILE – 2020 to 2023 tax years

T1135 – 2018 to 2023 tax years

Not supported for the 2020 to 2023 tax years:

Electronic transmission of Form T1134

Form T2203 – Provincial and Territorial Taxes - Multiple Jurisdictions

Form T1273 – Limited occurrences of Crop inventory valuation and productive capacity and Livestock inventory valuation

More than 4 Selected Financial Data (SFD) entries per self employment type

Forms T2091 – More than 3 SFD entries for Principle residence

Not supported for the 2019 tax year:

Form T2203 – Provincial and Territorial Taxes - Multiple Jurisdictions

Form T1273 – More than 15 occurrences under Limited occurrences of Crop inventory valuation and productive capacity and Livestock inventory valuation

More than 3 SFD entries per self employment type

Forms T2091 – More than 3 SFD entries for Principle residence

Amendment of the T1135

Not supported for the 2018 tax years:

Form T2203 – Provincial and Territorial Taxes - Multiple Jurisdictions

Form T1273 – More than 15 occurrences under Limited occurrences of Crop inventory valuation and productive capacity and Livestock inventory valuation

More than 3 SFD entries per self employment type

Amendment of the T1135

Product names:

TurboTax Free (Apple) Certified for the 2023 tax year

TurboTax Free (Android) Certified for the 2023 tax year

Support:

turbotax.ca/support

Available services:

Auto-fill my return – 2023 tax year

Express Notice of Assessment – 2023 tax year

ReFILE – 2023 tax year

T1135 – 2023 tax year

Not supported for the 2023 tax year:

Electronic transmission of Form T1134

Form T2203 – Provincial and Territorial Taxes – Multiple Jurisdictions

Form T1273 – Limited occurrences of Crop inventory valuation and productive capacity and Livestock inventory valuation

Please note that this information was provided by the software developer. If you find discrepancies in the information provided, please contact the software developer directly. The links are provided for your convenience and are to be used at your own discretion.
